{
  "stem": "22586.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he reported it to the authorities that my father made slanderous remarks against Hungarians, about the Hungarian government.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father was arrested.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And that was my first experience with anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] And I think it left my father very-- even after we had-- he had been released from jail, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he-- he was very worried and very afraid.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I guess he realized that this-- this is the way things are going to be and was very worried about it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think this about 1939 or '40, maybe 1940.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it certainly changed my father's life completely.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As far as we were concerned, we had to-- we couldn't go to public school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jewish people couldn't go to public school, so I went to the Hebrew gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think there were some other things also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you know, as-- as young people, we didn't really pay attention to-- we-- all my friends were Jewish, so I guess I was not as exposed to the anti-Semitism as some other people were.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but while under-- before 1938, I had never heard the word Jew mentioned.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean-- and-- and, of course, we had religious freedom, so it's not like we didn't have the religious freedom and that's why I didn't hear the word Jew.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But certainly under the Hungarians, there was an awful lot of anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even when we were taken away from home, I think that the Hungarians very willingly and fully cooperated with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were-- yes, my father was-- we were able to go to synagogues.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That-- that we were able to.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
